        <div class="noodlebar-logo"><img src="../images/ccd-logofood.jpg" class="scale"></div>
        <div class="foodsubhead">CAF&Eacute; COFFEE DAY</div>
        <div class="bodytext">Café Coffee Day is a coffee shop for the young and the young at heart. A smart, simple space that one can call their own for a while… sit down, talk and listen to conversations, hold short meetings or even have a lot of good
          fun…all over steaming cups of coffee.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="foodleft food-paddleft overflow-food">
        <a href="#"><img src="../images/ccdimg.jpg" class="scale"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="clr"></div>
    </div>
