      <div class="foodleft">
        <div class="noodlebar-logo"><img src="../images/mcd-foodlogo.jpg" class="scale"></div>
        <div class="foodsubhead">McDonalds</div>
        <div class="bodytext">Give in to your temptation of gorging upon those yummilicious burgers at McDonald's. Delivering smiles all across the world, McDonald's is one such brand that not only makes good food but wins heart as well. Choose from their
